48:20.579 --> 48:22.877
- You seem a little hyper.
- Had a couple Red Bulls.

48:23.048 --> 48:26.779
Ever had Red Bull? I never had Red Bull.
Had Red Bull last night. I like Red Bull.

48:26.952 --> 48:28.817
I got a new necklace. Glows in the dark.

48:28.988 --> 48:31.354
Can't really see it right now,
unless you do this.

48:31.524 --> 48:34.960
