Munchausen by Proxy.

58:03.628 --> 58:05.289
I'm your biggest fan. Bang!

58:05.464 --> 58:06.658
I killed her.

58:08.166 --> 58:09.428
I'm a somebody.

58:10.635 --> 58:12.830
